{"tid":1721010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(改良)(集思廣益)點樣起前一晚整定第二日早上嘅rb","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:20.000Z","uid":28240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba22331de9fb25b4cba47b20a1c1065d7fdce46a","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"以下五點係朝早難以造成大罷工嘅原因:<br />\n<br />\n-港奴搬磚<br />\n-黑社會出嚟晨運<br />\n-黑警半夜踢石仔<br />\n-手足連續咁多日早起太攰<br />\n-塞鐵唔係個個夠膽當住所有人面前做<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，依家成個旺角啲磚咁樣起法，都未成功罷工都已經變左做沙灘，見到咁多手足努力係好，但既然付出左努力就當然要有多啲回報啦<br />\n之前都有人開過post講半永久rb，主要都係鑽石屎地插釘，唔係唔得嘅，問題係呢啲咁技術性嘅嘢好難多人做<br />\n<br />\n我完全唔想講道德底線呢啲咁表皮嘅嘢，而家主要係想諗啲連女仔都能夠做到嘅半永久rb<br />\n<br />\n暫時我諗到嘅有英泥陣加釘，唔加釘都無所謂，可以用英泥堆搞到成條路凹凹凸凸，問題係需要時間風乾，要早啲set up，有冇人有其他方法？"},{"pid":"9b6e1502600a6b93013db2c3d861b7d90ac0db9e","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2889e0a44ed396235f9f137a874a77a82519dc9c","tid":1721010,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bc5af6c18953807deefddd4a2435a2b94a4ad45","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"大罷工"},{"pid":"a3abaf7fa85d64f0f94de9f73d8913e699fc211b","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deadf7ef38a075a80cdaaf98becfaa9e8da6659e","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a3a33c9a23b288390d8c4fbfebd559cf119ce7f","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3e2986be994a48a117c93ee51a2788d15c88c9c","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d575da6e706488abcbc246ec7c2b6ae360c9036","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc01a53d1ce030c49c65ffecf3ff612284cafff5","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f58099be74892bc497fa868cb7a793a2bbc30741","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e74bb925519de44d46dc9c2df4acec4d1d15043","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83e4feafbc787fda9c32a0743a605d8590c048bf","tid":1721010,"uid":28240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}